          "message": "The feature gate check was changed from `labs.isSet('welcomeEmails')` to `config.get('memberWelcomeEmailTestInbox')`. This replaces a boolean labs flag with a config value that is truthy when set. In production, if `memberWelcomeEmailTestInbox` is not configured, the entire welcome email job will be skipped, effectively disabling the feature for all members.",
