          "message": "The condition for triggering welcome email outbox creation was changed from `this._labsService.isSet('welcomeEmails') && WELCOME_EMAIL_SOURCES.includes(source)` to `welcomeEmailConfig || WELCOME_EMAIL_SOURCES.includes(source)`. When `welcomeEmailConfig` is truthy, the source check is bypassed, causing outbox entries to be created for any member source (e.g., admin-created, API-created) instead of only the allowed sources.",
